long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Wayback Machine Link-Checker is a browser extension that enables you to check if the webarchive - wayback machine as an older version of a link available. Simply right-click on a link and select the "Check Wayback Machine" submenu item. 

If you like the extention and find it useful - feel free to buy me a coffee and support me: https://bmc.link/gaidamarcel
